Cart Page : 

Move the calculation of gst, and delivery to the server


Checkout:

The cart data will be gathered in the server and formatted.

On Success{
1. First check the items quantities, if they are still available then go to 2. else goto 4.
2. create / update the  Order History of the user, also update the quantity of the items.
3. redirect back to cart and display success message. 

4. cancel the order, start the refund process, redirect back to cart and display item ran out of stock.
} 

On Cancel/ reject " redirect back to the cart and display Cancel message"
